---
title: Caribbean Pork Rissoles with Potato Wedges & Mango Mayonnaise
description: Add a medley of mild spice to your rissoles by giving them a little island flair! Straight from the Caribbean, this jerk seasoning brings unmistakeable flavour and fun to the humble rissole. Paired with a fresh garden salad and roasted wedges, this is a colourful take on the Aussie classic dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caribbean-pork-rissoles-cdf611c8.jpg
